<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />
</head>
<body>
  <%= render 'layouts/before_login_header' %>
  <%= render 'layouts/flash_messages' %>
    <div class="hero min-h-screen">
      <div class="hero-overlay">
        <div class="relative hero min-h-screen bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('images/worker2.jpeg');">
          <div class="bg-blue opacity-20 absolute inset-0"></div>
          <div class="hero-content text-center text-neutral-content">
            <div class="max-w-md">
              <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold text-white">シフト作成を自動化</h1>
              <p class="mb-5 text-black">介護施設に特化したシフト自動作成サービス<br>「Care Shift」です。</p>
              <%= link_to new_user_path, class: "btn btn-primary text-white rounded hover:bg-navy hover:underline px-10" do %>
                今すぐ登録
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <section class="border-b border-blue border-opacity-20">
    <div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-100 border-b-blue">
      <div class="w-screen max-w-6xl px-4 my-12">
        <div class="mb-8"></div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-24 text-center text-black">機能一覧</h2>
        <div class="tr-hero-content flex flex-col mb-24 lg:flex-row lg:justify-between">
          <div class="mr-24"><img src="images/shift-creat.png" alt="" class="border-blue border-4  border-opacity-50 rounded-md" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px;"></div>
          <div class="pt-4">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="40px" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="40px" fill="#807fe2">
                <path d="M710.83-106.83v-120h-120V-250h120v-120H734v120h120v23.17H734v120h-23.17ZM228.42-213.67q-22.73 0-38.82-16.09-16.1-16.1-16.1-38.88V-695.7q0-22.78 16.1-38.87 16.09-16.1 39.07-16.1h86.16v-88h27.84v88h198.66v-88h24.5v88h85.5q22.98 0 39.07 16.1 16.1 16.09 16.1 38.93V-461q-6.17 1-11.58.83-5.42-.16-11.59-.83v-68.67H196.67v260.84q0 12 10 22t22 10h270.66q0 5.83.17 11.58t-1.17 11.58H228.42Zm-31.75-339.16h486.66V-695.5q0-12-10-22t-22-10H228.67q-12 0-22 10t-10 22v142.67Zm0 0V-727.5v174.67Z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-navy text-sm font-medium ml-2 ">効率よく、時間短縮</p>
            </div>
              <h3 class="text-4xl mb-8 text-black">自動シフト作成</h3>
              <p class="text-gray mb-8">スタッフを追加し、勤務希望を入力します。その後 <br>シフト作成ボタンを押すだけで1ヶ月分のシフトを <br>自動で作成できます。夜勤の翌日は休み、最大5連勤までといった<br>制約を設けてシフト割り当てを行っています。誰でも簡単に、直感的に操作できます。</p>
              <%= link_to '登録はこちらから', new_user_path, class: 'text-blue text-sm hover:underline' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-b border-blue border-opacity-20">
    <div class="hero bg-base-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl px-4 my-12">
        <div class="tr-hero-content flex flex-col mb-24 lg:flex-row lg:justify-bitween mt-24">
          <div class="pt-4 mr-24">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="36px" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="36px" fill="#807fe2">
                <path d="M228.43-133.67q-22.74 0-38.83-16.09-16.1-16.1-16.1-38.84v-507.14q0-22.74 16.1-38.83 16.09-16.1 39.07-16.1h86.16v-88h27.84v88h278.66v-88h24.5v88h85.5q22.98 0 39.07 16.1 16.1 16.09 16.1 39.07v211.33h-23.17v-45.5H196.67v340.84q0 12 10 22t22 10H476v23.16H228.43Zm-31.76-419.16h566.66V-695.5q0-12-10-22t-22-10H228.67q-12 0-22 10t-10 22v142.67Zm0 0V-727.5v174.67Zm374.5 419.16v-77.83l210.81-209.81q4.85-4.52 10.05-6.02 5.2-1.5 9.9-1.5 4.67 0 10.12 2 5.45 2 9.78 5.83l37 37.67q3.27 5.21 5.39 10.35 2.11 5.15 2.11 9.73t-2.21 9.7q-2.22 5.11-5.26 9.58L649-133.67h-77.83Zm268-230-37-38 37 38Zm-240 202h37.6L781.5-306l-18.81-19-17.8-20-145.72 145.33v38ZM762.5-325l-18-20 37 39-19-19Z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-navy text-sm font-medium ml-2">簡単に、微調整が可能</p>
            </div>
              <h3 class="text-4xl mb-8 text-black">シフト編集</h3>
              <p class="text-gray mb-8">自動で作成したシフトも微調整したい時があると思います。シフトの微調整も、シフト編集ボタンから簡単に編集できます。</p>
              <%= link_to '登録はこちらから', new_user_path, class: 'text-blue text-sm hover:underline' %>
            </div>
          <div class=""><img src="images/shift-edit.png" alt="" class="border-blue border-4  border-opacity-50 rounded-md" style="width: 100%; max-width: 1000px;"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="border-b border-blue border-opacity-20">
    <div class="hero bg-base-100">
      <div class="max-w-6xl px-4 my-12">
        <div class="tr-hero-content flex flex-col mb-24 lg:flex-row lg:justify-bitween mt-24">
          <div class="mr-24"><img src="images/excel.png" alt="" class="border-blue border-4  border-opacity-50 rounded-md" style="width: 100%; max-width: 1000px;"></div>
          <div class="pt-4">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="40px" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" width="40px" fill="#807fe2">
                <path d="m480-360.5-111.5-112 13-10.5 90 90v-366H489v366l90-90 13 10.5-112 112ZM298.08-249q-21.02 0-35.05-14.18Q249-277.36 249-298.43v-41.07h17.5v41q0 12 10 22t22 10h363q12 0 22-10t10-22v-41H711v41.07q0 21.07-14.19 35.25Q682.61-249 661.6-249H298.08Z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-navy text-sm font-medium ml-2">Excelファイルをダウンロード</p>
            </div>
              <h3 class="text-4xl mb-8 text-black">エクセル出力機能</h3>
              <p class="text-gray mb-8">作成したシフトをエクセルファイルでダウンロードができます。ダウンロードしたエクセルファイルからシフトの編集、印刷を行うことができます。</p>
              <%= link_to '登録はこちらから', new_user_path, class: 'text-blue text-sm hover:underline' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%= render 'layouts/footer' %>
</body>
</html>